resolutions.title: GIP-91: Should the GnosisDAO onboard into Centrifuge Prime?
resolutions.excerpt: This proposal initiates the onboarding of GnosisDAO into Centrifuge Prime by investing ### of the treasury into Real-world assets (RWAs). The onboarding will be contingent upon the establishment of a Legal Conduit for GnosisDAO by Centrifuge for the safe investment of RWAs.
